### Gamification Engine API - Rules Management Endpoints
### Base URL: https://localhost:7000

### Get all rules
GET https://localhost:7000/api/rules
Accept: application/json

###

### Get active rules only
GET https://localhost:7000/api/rules/active
Accept: application/json

###

### Get rules by trigger event type
GET https://localhost:7000/api/rules/trigger/USER_COMMENTED
Accept: application/json

###

### Get specific rule by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/rules/rule123
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new rule
POST https://localhost:7000/api/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "rule123",
  "name": "First Comment Reward",
  "description": "Award 10 XP for first comment",
  "isActive": true,
  "triggers": ["USER_COMMENTED"],
  "conditions": [
    {
      "type": "firstOccurrence",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ],
  "rewards": [
    {
      "type": "points",
      "targetId": "xp",
      "amount": 10,
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}

###

### Update an existing rule
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/rules/rule123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "First Comment Reward (Updated)",
  "description": "Award 15 XP for first comment",
  "isActive": true,
  "triggers": ["USER_COMMENTED"],
  "conditions": [
    {
      "type": "firstOccurrence",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ],
  "rewards": [
    {
      "type": "points",
      "targetId": "xp",
      "amount": 15,
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}

###

### Activate a rule
POST https://localhost:7000/api/rules/rule123/activate
Accept: application/json

###

### Deactivate a rule
POST https://localhost:7000/api/rules/rule123/deactivate
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete a rule
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/rules/rule123
Accept: application/json

